{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_07_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 求められているものは？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1466.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "アンケートを書き終わったので\n{user}さんのデスクに置いておきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've finished writing the survey‚\nand I left it on your desk‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、後で読ませてもらうよ\nその様子だと満足のいく回答が書けたみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ I'll read it later.\nIt seems like you wrote satisfactory answers judging by your expression.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.6666662375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。サニピのみんなに相談しながら書いたので\n私のイメージにあった答えが出来たと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I think so too. I wrote answers that matched my image\nwhile consulting with everyone at Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに相談してアンケートを書いたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you write the survey after consulting with everyone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6666662375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.7999995708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。手伝ってもらってアイドルの一ノ瀬怜らしい\n答えを考えたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. With their help‚ I was able to come up with answers\nthat suit Rei Ichinose‚ the idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9899.999999999998,
          "startTime": 40.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0333329041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私は今からレッスンがあるので\n後で感想を聞かせて下さい。それでは、失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a lesson now‚\nso please let me know your thoughts later. Well then‚ excuse me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.6333313782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルらしい答えか……。少し気になるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Answers befitting an idol… That's interesting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6333313782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の午後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The afternoon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1666647116,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1333.3352884000008,
          "startTime": 48.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2666647116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "あの……アンケートのことで\n聞きたいことがあるって、なんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… about the survey‚\nwas there something you wanted to ask?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0333299715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "私の答えにおかしなところがありましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Any strange points about my answers?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5000010967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "おかしいというか、読んでいて違和感があったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that it was strange‚ but it felt off while reading it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5666677634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、「理想の告白のされ方」という質問だが\n前は違う答えを書いていなかったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ there's a question about \"ideal way to be asked out‚\"\nand didn't you write a different answer before?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5666618348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。最初はシンプルに「好きです」と\n言われたいですって書いてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ at first‚ I wrote simply that\nI want to be told 'I like you.'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3999951681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだとファンが私に期待している答えとは\n違うと思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I thought that answer didn't match\nwhat fans expect from me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1666618348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "私から告白された方がファンは嬉しいですよね？\nそれに、その方がゲームも盛り上がるはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fans would be happier if I ask them out instead‚ right?\nPlus‚ it would make the game more exciting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8333285015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームが盛り上がるから？\nもしかして他の答えも同じように考えたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because it would make the game more exciting?\nDid you think the same way about other answers too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7999951681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、どうすればファンが喜ぶかを第一に考えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I thought about what would make the fans happy first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3666652203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "ファンが思い描くアイドル一ノ瀬怜のイメージに\nあった答えを書いたんですが、どうでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wrote answers that matched the image of idol Rei Ichinose\nthat fans envision. But how about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9385705815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことか……\n俺が感じた違和感の正体が分かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nI've figured out what was bothering me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3333285015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "この回答は、空気を読んで、周囲の顔色をうかがって\n周りに合わせた答えだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These answers are just trying to read the room and\nothers' mind‚ and adapt to the atmosphere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5666608175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "周りに合わせた答え……でも、それが\nファンの期待に応えるってことじゃないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Adapting to the atmosphere… But\nIsn't that about meeting the fans' expectations?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8666608175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが求めているのはアイドルの私です\n素の私じゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't everyone expecting the idol me?\nNot the real me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1666608175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それは違う。このゲームを遊ぶファンはアイドルと\n恋をしたいんじゃない。一ノ瀬怜と恋をしたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not it. Fans playing this game don't want to fall in love with\njust any idol. They want to fall in love with Rei Ichinose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1681948026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "だから変に取り繕わなくていい。ファンのみんなも\n等身大の、ありのままの怜を望んでいるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ you don't have to make up yourself.\nFans want the real‚ true Rei. They want the real you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0999941509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "ありのままの私をファンが望んでる……\nそうだったんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The real me… That's what the fans want…\nI see… That's what it was…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.9666608175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "正直に言うと、心のどこかで引っかかっていたんです\n本当にこれでいいのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I had doubts somewhere in my heart.\nI wondered if this was really okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3666608175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの人を喜ばせたいって気持ちが\n大きくなり過ぎて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My desire to make fans happy got too big‚\nand as a result‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.9999941509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_02-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "結果的にファンが求めているものから\n遠ざかっていたんですね……",
      "translations": {
